'''Chris Cowdrill''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed [[Jeigh Esse]] and the [[Stellan (species)|Stellan]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was picked Second Place in the under-sixteen years old category. He was fifteen at the time his entry was published.

